# game/script/hwb_s25a.rpy:47
translate spanish hwb_s25a_1ec7356b:

    # "Outside, I take Marina's hand, but it feels limp inside my own."
    "Afuera, tomo la mano de Marina, pero se siente inerte dentro de la mía."

# game/script/hwb_s25a.rpy:49
translate spanish hwb_s25a_01cf9107:

    # "I let her lead the way down the street and towards the busiest part of the city."
    "La dejo guiarme calle abajo hacia la parte más concurrida de la ciudad."

# game/script/hwb_s25a.rpy:51
translate spanish hwb_s25a_47225ed2:

    # "Sometimes stuff on the side catches her eye. Brightly colored sports cars that probably belong to millionaires pass by us pretty frequently."
    "A veces, algo a un lado llama su atención. Autos deportivos de colores brillantes, que probablemente pertenecen a millonarios, pasan junto a nosotras con bastante frecuencia."

# game/script/hwb_s25a.rpy:53
translate spanish hwb_s25a_4667f55c:

    # "There are also people in bike-drawn carriages, and double-decker tour buses."
    "También hay carruajes tirados por bicicletas y autobuses turísticos de dos pisos."

# game/script/hwb_s25a.rpy:55
translate spanish hwb_s25a_1d535d7b:

    # "Besides the people, the buildings themselves all compete to stand out. Almost every storefront has something neon, flashing to get you to look at it."
    "Además de la gente, los propios edificios compiten por destacarse. Casi todos los escaparates tienen algo de neón que parpadea para que lo mires."

# game/script/hwb_s25a.rpy:57
translate spanish hwb_s25a_a598f627:

    # "Toy stores, restaurants, sex shops and more all vie for real estate. Within a two-block radius, you could probably buy anything you ever wanted."
    "Tiendas de juguetes, restaurantes, sex shops y más compiten por el espacio. En un radio de dos cuadras, probablemente podrías comprar cualquier cosa que hayas deseado."

# game/script/hwb_s25a.rpy:59
translate spanish hwb_s25a_dd49bef9:

    # "Maybe a half-mile ahead of us, on the other side of the road, there are a few street vendors on the sidewalk."
    "Tal vez a media milla de nosotras, al otro lado de la calle, hay algunos vendedores ambulantes en la acera."

# game/script/hwb_s25a.rpy:61
translate spanish hwb_s25a_3be69a20:

    # "They have awnings set up to shade themselves and their merchandise, though it’s too far away to see what they’re selling."
    "Tienen toldos instalados para protegerse del sol y proteger su mercancía, aunque está demasiado lejos para ver qué venden."

# game/script/hwb_s25a.rpy:63
translate spanish hwb_s25a_24e75d82:

    # "Marina spots them and points."
    "Marina los ve y señala."

# game/script/hwb_s25a.rpy:68
translate spanish hwb_s25a_ac097ff1:

    # Marina "Ooh, let’s go look!"
    Marina "Ох, пойдем посмотрим!"

# game/script/hwb_s25a.rpy:70
translate spanish hwb_s25a_d03e2b5f:

    # "But then her excitement vanishes."
    "Pero entonces su emoción se desvanece."

# game/script/hwb_s25a.rpy:74
translate spanish hwb_s25a_522d8d43:

    # Marina "Um, I mean, if you want to."
    Marina "Эм, я имела ввиду, если ты хочешь."

# game/script/hwb_s25a.rpy:79
translate spanish hwb_s25a_e246048a:

    # Amber "Yeah, let’s check it out!"
    Amber "Ага, пойдем поглядим!"

# game/script/hwb_s25a.rpy:86
translate spanish hwb_s25a_e7ff5de8:

    # "With a hopeful smile, Marina starts to run. A red light at the crosswalk makes her stop not too far ahead, though."
    "Con una sonrisa esperanzada, Marina empieza a correr. Sin embargo, un semáforo en rojo en el cruce peatonal la detiene no muy adelante."

# game/script/hwb_s25a.rpy:91
translate spanish hwb_s25a_99564d9b:

    # "I catch up just in time for the light to change."
    "La alcanzo justo a tiempo para que el semáforo cambie."

# game/script/hwb_s25a.rpy:95
translate spanish hwb_s25a_838b4c3a:

    # "Before she can dart away, I take Marina’s hand. She doesn’t object, but searches my face. So I smile, and she smiles back."
    "Antes de que pueda salir disparada, tomo la mano de Marina. Ella no se opone, pero escudriña mi rostro. Así que sonrío, y ella me devuelve la sonrisa."

# game/script/hwb_s25a.rpy:97
translate spanish hwb_s25a_3a6cfe76:

    # "I let her pull me to the vendor, who seems to be selling a little bit of everything."
    "Dejo que me arrastre hasta el vendedor, que parece vender un poco de todo."

# game/script/hwb_s25a.rpy:99
translate spanish hwb_s25a_c8a758c3:

    # "T-shirts cover most of a wire rack that serves as a wall. There are also bins of buttons, keychains, and other small trinkets."
    "Camisetas cubren la mayor parte de un estante de alambre que sirve como pared. También hay cestas de botones, llaveros y otras baratijas pequeñas."

# game/script/hwb_s25a.rpy:103
translate spanish hwb_s25a_be32ea25:

    # "One bin is full of tiny soapstone animal carvings, and those are what Marina goes for."
    "Una cesta está llena de pequeñas figuras talladas en esteatita, y esas son las que Marina busca."

# game/script/hwb_s25a.rpy:105
translate spanish hwb_s25a_a260d352:

    # "I ignore the vendor and his weasely small talk, refusing to be conned into buying tons of junk."
    "Ignoro al vendedor y su charla insinuante, negándome a dejarme estafar para comprar un montón de chatarra."

# game/script/hwb_s25a.rpy:111
translate spanish hwb_s25a_3d108b78:

    # "After a minute, Marina selects a little stone coyote. I pay five bucks for it; practically robbery."
    "Después de un minuto, Marina elige un pequeño coyote de piedra. Pago cinco dólares por él; prácticamente un robo."

# game/script/hwb_s25a.rpy:121
translate spanish hwb_s25a_910bd25f:

    # "We start down the road again, with Marina inspecting her new treasure."
    "Empezamos a caminar de nuevo por la calle, mientras Marina inspecciona su nuevo tesoro."

# game/script/hwb_s25a.rpy:125
translate spanish hwb_s25a_8cd4c588:

    # Amber "Why a coyote?"
    Amber "Почему именно койот?"

# game/script/hwb_s25a.rpy:131
translate spanish hwb_s25a_4075b791:

    # Marina "I thought she was the cutest. Look at the way the color changes here."
    Marina "По-моему, он был самым миленьким. Смотри, как он переливается на свету."

# game/script/hwb_s25a.rpy:133
translate spanish hwb_s25a_bcb4aa7e:

    # "She holds the little trinket up by my nose. There’s a spot where the color changes from brown to a milky white on one side of its face."
    "Sostiene la pequeña baratija frente a mi nariz. Hay una mancha donde el color cambia de marrón a un blanco lechoso en un lado de su cara."

# game/script/hwb_s25a.rpy:137
translate spanish hwb_s25a_182a1c42:

    # Amber "That is pretty."
    Amber "Он чудный."

# game/script/hwb_s25a.rpy:139
translate spanish hwb_s25a_a33fe3d8:

    # Marina "Mhm. Plus, wolves are pretty much my favorite animal and coyotes are close enough."
    Marina "Хмм. К тому же мое любимое животное это волк, а койот на него сильно похож."

# game/script/hwb_s25a.rpy:143
translate spanish hwb_s25a_89cc2402:

    # Amber "Yeah? Have you ever seen a live wolf?"
    Amber "Да? А ты когда-нибудь видела волка вживую?"

# game/script/hwb_s25a.rpy:147
translate spanish hwb_s25a_47113f2a:

    # Marina "No, I wish. You?"
    Marina "Нет, но очень хотела бы. А ты?"

# game/script/hwb_s25a.rpy:151
translate spanish hwb_s25a_57c82d5d:

    # Amber "At Yellowstone a couple years ago, yeah. I begged Gramps to take me."
    Amber "Ага, пару лет назад в Йеллоустонском парке. Я просто умоляла дедушку отвезти меня туда."

# game/script/hwb_s25a.rpy:155
translate spanish hwb_s25a_f16d8ef5:

    # "As soon as I mention Gramps’ name, I see Marina’s eyes flit towards mine."
    "En cuanto menciono el nombre del Abuelo, veo que los ojos de Marina se desvían hacia los míos."

# game/script/hwb_s25a.rpy:157
translate spanish hwb_s25a_d4c48c01:

    # Marina "What else do they have there?"
    Marina "А что еще там было?"

# game/script/hwb_s25a.rpy:161
translate spanish hwb_s25a_68815d42:

    # Amber "All kinds of stuff. Wolves, bears, buffalo, elk, deer. Pretty much any kind of forest animal."
    Amber "Да много чего. Волки, медведи, лоси, олени. Думаю, любые лесные животные."

# game/script/hwb_s25a.rpy:165
translate spanish hwb_s25a_7eba76b5:

    # Marina "And they just wander around, right?"
    Marina "И они просто бродят там, да?"

# game/script/hwb_s25a.rpy:167
translate spanish hwb_s25a_e75e62be:

    # Amber "Yeah, there are even places where you can feed some of them out of your car."
    Amber "Ага, там даже есть специальное место, где можно  покормить некоторых животных, не выходя из машины."

# game/script/hwb_s25a.rpy:171
translate spanish hwb_s25a_7a799617:

    # Marina "What about the meat-eaters? Like wolves and stuff."
    Marina "А что насчет плотоядных? Вроде волков и прочих?"

# game/script/hwb_s25a.rpy:175
translate spanish hwb_s25a_ddfddf4c:

    # Amber "There are spots where you can see them but you can’t feed ‘em. They’re still wild animals. It’s not a zoo or anything."
    Amber "Там есть места, откуда можно за ними понаблюдать, но кормить нельзя. Они все же дикие животные. Это же не зоопарк."

# game/script/hwb_s25a.rpy:179
translate spanish hwb_s25a_a122ba13:

    # Marina "I wanna go there someday."
    Marina "Хотела бы я туда попасть как-нибудь."

# game/script/hwb_s25a.rpy:183
translate spanish hwb_s25a_017aaa1b:

    # Amber "I’ll take you to see them sometime. It’s a cool place."
    Amber "Когда-нибудь съездим туда. Это крутое место."

# game/script/hwb_s25a.rpy:185
translate spanish hwb_s25a_cee675b3:

    # Marina "Really?"
    Marina "Правда?"

# game/script/hwb_s25a.rpy:189
translate spanish hwb_s25a_e5bf5a31:

    # Amber "Yeah, sure."
    Amber "Да, конечно."

# game/script/hwb_s25a.rpy:194
translate spanish hwb_s25a_3af6aac1:

    # Amber "We need to give ourselves ample room for sequels."
    Amber "Надо бы позаботиться о том, чтобы у нас было достаточно возможностей для подобных путешествий."

# game/script/hwb_s25a.rpy:198
translate spanish hwb_s25a_87bf8300:

    # "I try to play it off like it’s not a big deal to me. But talking about future plans - anything that would happen after the festival - ignites that sense of uncertainty in my chest."
    "Intento fingir que no es un gran problema para mí. Pero hablar de planes futuros, cualquier cosa que suceda después del festival, enciende esa sensación de incertidumbre en mi pecho."

# game/script/hwb_s25a.rpy:200
translate spanish hwb_s25a_67fd4545:

    # "The way her eyes light up when I promise to take her both soothes and agitates the feeling."
    "La forma en que sus ojos se iluminan cuando le prometo llevarla calma y agita esa sensación a la vez."

# game/script/hwb_s25a.rpy:204
translate spanish hwb_s25a_8b473b35:

    # "No matter what, I’m happy that she’s happy."
    "Pase lo que pase, me alegra que ella esté feliz."

# game/script/hwb_s25a.rpy:208
translate spanish hwb_s25a_c20e4b52:

    # "I follow behind as she darts from stall to stall like a hummingbird."
    "La sigo mientras revolotea de puesto en puesto como un colibrí."

# game/script/hwb_s25a.rpy:210
translate spanish hwb_s25a_6db6c0ea:

    # "They all offer more of the same: generic desert-themed trinkets or gaudy ‘I Love Las Vegas’ merchandise."
    "Todos ofrecen más de lo mismo: baratijas genéricas con temática del desierto o mercancía llamativa de 'Amo Las Vegas'."

# game/script/hwb_s25a.rpy:212
translate spanish hwb_s25a_8e92bc90:

    # "The sidewalks are full of these vendors, who shout and try to get the attention of all the dozens of people who pass by. Marina’s the only one who gets hooked in."
    "Las aceras están llenas de estos vendedores, que gritan y tratan de llamar la atención de las docenas de personas que pasan. Marina es la única que se engancha."

# game/script/hwb_s25a.rpy:214
translate spanish hwb_s25a_50132bff:

    # "But she doesn’t ask for anything else. Maybe there just isn’t enough wolf merchandise."
    "Pero no pide nada más. Quizás simplemente no hay suficiente mercancía de lobos."

# game/script/hwb_s25a.rpy:218
translate spanish hwb_s25a_328882be:

    # "Every time she dives in to examine someone’s wares, I hang back with my hands in my pockets and watch. Once she’s done, we hold hands again."
    "Cada vez que se lanza a examinar las mercancías de alguien, yo me quedo atrás con las manos en los bolsillos y observo. Cuando termina, nos tomamos de las manos otra vez."

# game/script/hwb_s25a.rpy:222
translate spanish hwb_s25a_61bf52e8:

    # "It’s a nice cycle."
    "Es un ciclo agradable."

# game/script/hwb_s25a.rpy:224
translate spanish hwb_s25a_6b1d06b4:

    # "But all that changes once we reach the Strip itself, with its eclectic architecture and eccentric population."
    "Pero todo eso cambia cuando llegamos al Strip en sí, con su arquitectura ecléctica y su población excéntrica."

# game/script/hwb_s25a.rpy:226
translate spanish hwb_s25a_e9dee4af:

    # "I point out some of the more famous places, like the Luxor, which is shaped like a pyramid, and Caesar’s Palace, which looks like it was stolen from Rome."
    "Señalo algunos de los lugares más famosos, como el Luxor, que tiene forma de pirámide, y el Caesar's Palace, que parece robado de Roma."

# game/script/hwb_s25a.rpy:230
translate spanish hwb_s25a_9fca9677:

    # "Marina ‘ooh’s’ and ‘aah’s’ in all the right places, though to my surprise she doesn’t try to lead us to them."
    "Marina hace 'ooh' y 'aah' en los momentos adecuados, aunque para mi sorpresa, no intenta llevarnos hacia ellos."

# game/script/hwb_s25a.rpy:234
translate spanish hwb_s25a_110da412:

    # "Instead, she seems dead-set on taking us further and further down the row of sidewalk salesmen, like she’s looking for something in particular."
    "En cambio, parece empeñada en llevarnos cada vez más lejos por la fila de vendedores ambulantes, como si buscara algo en particular."

# game/script/hwb_s25a.rpy:236
translate spanish hwb_s25a_bd1edf9b:

    # "Not that I have any idea what that is."
    "No es que tenga idea de qué es eso."

# game/script/hwb_s25a.rpy:238
translate spanish hwb_s25a_65e7d802:

    # "She leads the way, looking from side to side, but never seeming quite to find it."
    "Ella guía el camino, mirando de un lado a otro, pero nunca parece encontrarlo del todo."

# game/script/hwb_s25a.rpy:242
translate spanish hwb_s25a_4bbf201e:

    # "Until suddenly, she freezes in place. A large wave of pedestrian traffic behind us crests and spills around like we’re not even there."
    "Hasta que, de repente, se congela en su lugar. Una gran ola de tráfico peatonal detrás de nosotros se eleva y se derrama a nuestro alrededor como si no estuviéramos allí."

# game/script/hwb_s25a.rpy:244
translate spanish hwb_s25a_3cff14d3:

    # "Marina points ahead at one of the street vendors a few blocks ahead."
    "Marina señala hacia adelante a uno de los vendedores callejeros a unas cuadras de distancia."

# game/script/hwb_s25a.rpy:248
translate spanish hwb_s25a_a8e0bf68:

    # Marina "Found one!"
    Marina "Нашла!"

# game/script/hwb_s25a.rpy:250
translate spanish hwb_s25a_591d31ec:

    # "I’m yanked forward once again, being dragged by her newfound enthusiasm."
    "Me jalan hacia adelante otra vez, arrastrada por su renovado entusiasmo."

# game/script/hwb_s25a.rpy:252
translate spanish hwb_s25a_564acde3:

    # "Rather than a bunch of cheaply made goods, the merchant she's noticed has a bunch of colored drawings of cartoon characters - barely recognizable due to the exaggerated style."
    "En lugar de un montón de productos baratos, el comerciante que ella notó tiene un montón de dibujos coloreados de personajes de caricaturas, apenas reconocibles por el estilo exagerado."

# game/script/hwb_s25a.rpy:254
translate spanish hwb_s25a_ebf3ba19:

    # "A sign beside them advertises, ‘Custom commissions - $30 each.’"
    "Un letrero junto a ellos anuncia: 'Comisiones personalizadas - $30 cada una'."

# game/script/hwb_s25a.rpy:258
translate spanish hwb_s25a_25bf8563:

    # "I immediately understand what it is Marina wants."
    "Inmediatamente entiendo lo que Marina quiere."

# game/script/hwb_s25a.rpy:262
translate spanish hwb_s25a_dc0c4993:

    # Amber "No. No, no no."
    Amber "Нет. Нет, и еще раз нет."

# game/script/hwb_s25a.rpy:270
translate spanish hwb_s25a_1932b840:

    # "I try to drag my heels, but I’m tugged along by Marina. She’s surprisingly strong when she wants to be."
    "Intento frenar, pero soy arrastrada por Marina. Es sorprendentemente fuerte cuando quiere."

# game/script/hwb_s25a.rpy:274
translate spanish hwb_s25a_a13e128c:

    # Marina "Amber."
    Marina "Эмбер."

# game/script/hwb_s25a.rpy:276
translate spanish hwb_s25a_b543f6e6:

    # "She says my name without even turning around."
    "Dice mi nombre sin siquiera darse la vuelta."

# game/script/hwb_s25a.rpy:278
translate spanish hwb_s25a_4263600a:

    # Marina "This has been on my bucket list for years."
    Marina "Это было в моем списке желаний на протяжении стольких лет."

# game/script/hwb_s25a.rpy:282
translate spanish hwb_s25a_4bc373ab:

    # Marina "It’s happening."
    Marina "И вот это случилось."

# game/script/hwb_s25a.rpy:286
translate spanish hwb_s25a_2fce848c:

    # Amber "What has? Getting ripped off by a street artist?"
    Amber "Случилось что? Твоя мечта – быть облапошенной  уличным художником?"

# game/script/hwb_s25a.rpy:290
translate spanish hwb_s25a_3815f31e:

    # Marina "Having someone draw me!"
    Marina "Нет, я хочу, чтобы кто-нибудь меня нарисовал!"

# game/script/hwb_s25a.rpy:294
translate spanish hwb_s25a_4247638c:

    # "My protests going ignored, I fall in step and accept my fate."
    "Mis protestas siendo ignoradas, me pongo al paso y acepto mi destino."

# game/script/hwb_s25a.rpy:296
translate spanish hwb_s25a_723150ec:

    # "The guy manning the booth looks like he's completely out of place: he’s wearing a flashy Hawaiian shirt and a baseball cap."
    "El tipo que atiende el puesto parece completamente fuera de lugar: lleva una camisa hawaiana llamativa y una gorra de béisbol."

# game/script/hwb_s25a.rpy:298
translate spanish hwb_s25a_278b6cd1:

    # "When he notices Marina and I approaching, he sits up from his slouching position and grins."
    "Cuando nota que Marina y yo nos acercamos, se endereza de su posición encorvada y sonríe."

# game/script/hwb_s25a.rpy:300
translate spanish hwb_s25a_0f275fee:

    # Artist "Hello, ladies!"
    Artist "Здравствуйте, дамы!"

# game/script/hwb_s25a.rpy:305
translate spanish hwb_s25a_bbdcf5d3:

    # Marina "Hi there! We were interested in having our portrait drawn."
    Marina "Привет! Нам бы хотелось, что бы вы нарисовали наши портреты."

# game/script/hwb_s25a.rpy:309
translate spanish hwb_s25a_52ba7651:

    # "\"We\" weren’t. {i}You{/i} were."
    "\"Nosotros\" no estábamos. {i}Tú{/i} estabas."

# game/script/hwb_s25a.rpy:311
translate spanish hwb_s25a_7b4e6fc2:

    # "But I don’t protest. I’ve resigned myself to going along with whatever she wanted."
    "Pero no protesto. Me he resignado a seguir adelante con lo que ella quisiera."

# game/script/hwb_s25a.rpy:315
translate spanish hwb_s25a_1b511cf5:

    # Artist "Perfect."
    Artist "Прекрасно."

# game/script/hwb_s25a.rpy:317
translate spanish hwb_s25a_530b7869:

    # "He frames us with his fingers, like he’s going to take a picture."
    "Nos encuadra con los dedos, como si fuera a tomar una foto."

# game/script/hwb_s25a.rpy:319
translate spanish hwb_s25a_f3cbc553:

    # Artist "You girls stand right there and get comfy. I’ll get ready."
    Artist "Вы, девушки, устраивайтесь вон там поудобней, а я пока подготовлюсь."

# game/script/hwb_s25a.rpy:321
translate spanish hwb_s25a_318af9eb:

    # "He lurches off his wooden chair and grabs a sketchpad and a box of pencils."
    "Se levanta de su silla de madera y agarra un bloc de dibujo y una caja de lápices."

# game/script/hwb_s25a.rpy:323
translate spanish hwb_s25a_adacfde9:

    # Artist "We’ll do you two in color, how’s that sound?"
    Artist "Я нарисую вас обеих в цвете, согласны?"

# game/script/hwb_s25a.rpy:327
translate spanish hwb_s25a_3b2f38f7:

    # Marina "Great!"
    Marina "Великолепно!"

# game/script/hwb_s25a.rpy:329
translate spanish hwb_s25a_76285873:

    # "I just grimace."
    "Solo hago una mueca."

# game/script/hwb_s25a.rpy:331
translate spanish hwb_s25a_d660593c:

    # "I’m not fond of having my picture taken, and this isn’t much better."
    "No me gusta que me tomen fotos, y esto no es mucho mejor."

# game/script/hwb_s25a.rpy:333
translate spanish hwb_s25a_98bc6251:

    # "I just never feel satisfied with how I look."
    "Simplemente nunca me siento satisfecha con mi apariencia."

# game/script/hwb_s25a.rpy:335
translate spanish hwb_s25a_7e47d4f7:

    # "That’s why there aren’t many pictures of Gramps and me. Just a couple."
    "Por eso no hay muchas fotos del abuelo y mías. Solo un par."

# game/script/hwb_s25a.rpy:337
translate spanish hwb_s25a_ebd928db:

    # "I’ll deal with it, for Marina’s sake."
    "Lo soportaré, por Marina."

# game/script/hwb_s25a.rpy:341
translate spanish hwb_s25a_c73e66f4:

    # "We stand under an awning, though its shade does little to help the heat. Marina shifts from foot to foot while I just wait with my hands in my pockets."
    "Nos paramos bajo un toldo, aunque su sombra apenas alivia el calor. Marina cambia el peso de un pie al otro mientras yo solo espero con las manos en los bolsillos."

# game/script/hwb_s25a.rpy:345
translate spanish hwb_s25a_a0dd852e:

    # "Every so often, she turns to beam at me, though she doesn’t say anything."
    "De vez en cuando, se voltea para sonreírme radiante, aunque no dice nada."

# game/script/hwb_s25a.rpy:347
translate spanish hwb_s25a_973bc217:

    # "Geez. Not sure why she’s so hyped up, but it’s cute."
    "Cielos. No sé por qué está tan emocionada, pero es lindo."

# game/script/hwb_s25a.rpy:351
translate spanish hwb_s25a_c055925f:

    # "The guy finally gets his stuff ready, all set up an easel. The piece of paper he’s using is almost the size of my torso."
    "El tipo por fin prepara sus cosas, colocando un caballete. El papel que usa es casi del tamaño de mi torso."

# game/script/hwb_s25a.rpy:353
translate spanish hwb_s25a_54a366b8:

    # Artist "Go ahead and scrunch together now."
    Artist "А теперь встаньте вместе."

# game/script/hwb_s25a.rpy:355
translate spanish hwb_s25a_2b9f81a3:

    # "He makes a motion with his hands."
    "Hace un gesto con las manos."

# game/script/hwb_s25a.rpy:364
translate spanish hwb_s25a_be124736:

    # "Marina stands near me, and I wrap one arm around her."
    "Marina se para cerca de mí, y la rodeo con un brazo."

# game/script/hwb_s25a.rpy:366
translate spanish hwb_s25a_693e4436:

    # Artist "Closer."
    Artist "Ближе."

# game/script/hwb_s25a.rpy:380
translate spanish hwb_s25a_1025978c:

    # "Our shoulders are touching."
    "Nuestros hombros se tocan."

# game/script/hwb_s25a.rpy:382
translate spanish hwb_s25a_90361038:

    # Artist "Closerrrrr."
    Artist "Блииииже."

# game/script/hwb_s25a.rpy:396
translate spanish hwb_s25a_18d65364:

    # "Now we’re cheek to cheek."
    "Ahora estamos mejilla con mejilla."

# game/script/hwb_s25a.rpy:398
translate spanish hwb_s25a_1b511cf5_1:

    # Artist "Perfect."
    Artist "Идеально."

# game/script/hwb_s25a.rpy:400
translate spanish hwb_s25a_c8e6ab1e:

    # "And he stares at us with a smile for just a second longer than is comfortable. It makes his expression seem more than a little sleazy."
    "Y él nos mira con una sonrisa por un segundo más de lo cómodo. Eso hace que su expresión parezca más que un poco desagradable."

# game/script/hwb_s25a.rpy:402
translate spanish hwb_s25a_d7414c85:

    # "Before I can change my mind, he looks down at the paper and starts to draw."
    "Antes de que pueda cambiar de opinión, baja la mirada al papel y empieza a dibujar."

# game/script/hwb_s25a.rpy:404
translate spanish hwb_s25a_69f2f645:

    # "We stand there, not talking or moving at all."
    "Nos quedamos ahí, sin hablar ni movernos en absoluto."

# game/script/hwb_s25a.rpy:408
translate spanish hwb_s25a_a62a0e7e:

    # "Once, Marina starts to ask something, but he waves his hand without even looking up."
    "Una vez, Marina empieza a preguntar algo, pero él agita la mano sin siquiera levantar la vista."

# game/script/hwb_s25a.rpy:410
translate spanish hwb_s25a_34b5b9a9:

    # Artist "Quiet! If you move, you’ll mess it all up."
    Artist "Тихо! Если шевельнетесь, то все испортите."

# game/script/hwb_s25a.rpy:414
translate spanish hwb_s25a_d4507e52:

    # "So she shuts up. I can feel her jaw snap shut since it’s smooshed against my own."
    "Así que se calla. Puedo sentir su mandíbula cerrarse de golpe porque está aplastada contra la mía."

# game/script/hwb_s25a.rpy:416
translate spanish hwb_s25a_9ee6ec61:

    # "Fifteen minutes pass. My mouth is starting to get sore. I didn’t have any guesses as to how long this would take, but it’s starting to get annoying."
    "Pasan quince minutos. Mi boca empieza a doler. No tenía idea de cuánto tiempo tomaría esto, pero ya está empezando a ser molesto."

# game/script/hwb_s25a.rpy:424
translate spanish hwb_s25a_8ba66404:

    # "Even Marina seems to be having second thoughts. She wriggles, just barely, probably to fight the growing tension in her muscles."
    "Hasta Marina parece estar arrepintiéndose. Se retuerce, apenas, probablemente para combatir la tensión creciente en sus músculos."

# game/script/hwb_s25a.rpy:426
translate spanish hwb_s25a_8eb15232:

    # "Not enough to ruin the drawing though."
    "Pero no lo suficiente como para arruinar el dibujo."

# game/script/hwb_s25a.rpy:428
translate spanish hwb_s25a_a89c2c2e:

    # "From the corner of my eye, I notice a couple of the glances that we get. We probably don’t look especially out of place, but more like hapless tourists who get conned into something."
    "Por el rabillo del ojo, noto un par de miradas que recibimos. Probablemente no parecemos especialmente fuera de lugar, sino más bien como turistas desventurados que cayeron en una estafa."

# game/script/hwb_s25a.rpy:430
translate spanish hwb_s25a_f9bf36f9:

    # "I guess we are, to an extent."
    "Supongo que lo somos, hasta cierto punto."

# game/script/hwb_s25a.rpy:432
translate spanish hwb_s25a_229171b9:

    # "I wouldn’t mind, except that we also look ridiculous being stuck together like nearly-Siamese twins."
    "No me importaría, excepto que también nos vemos ridículas pegadas como siamesas casi unidas."

# game/script/hwb_s25a.rpy:434
translate spanish hwb_s25a_2f0f5395:

    # "Our artist draws with long, swift strokes. Though I can’t see what he’s doing, he appears confident. Hopefully the result is worth the discomfort."
    "Nuestro artista dibuja con trazos largos y rápidos. Aunque no puedo ver lo que hace, parece seguro. Espero que el resultado valga la incomodidad."

# game/script/hwb_s25a.rpy:436
translate spanish hwb_s25a_2a86c054:

    # "And the thirty bucks."
    "Y los treinta dólares."

# game/script/hwb_s25a.rpy:438
translate spanish hwb_s25a_5020f790:

    # "I’m nearly at my breaking point when he finally leans back and sets his pencils aside."
    "Estoy casi al límite cuando finalmente se reclina y deja los lápices a un lado."

# game/script/hwb_s25a.rpy:440
translate spanish hwb_s25a_3edf8561:

    # Artist "Done!"
    Artist "Готово!"

# game/script/hwb_s25a.rpy:456
translate spanish hwb_s25a_29a357e7:

    # "Marina peels away from me instantly, leaving a damp spot of shared sweat on my face. I rub at it as I follow her, more slowly, to see the results."
    "Marina se separa de mí al instante, dejando una mancha húmeda de sudor compartido en mi cara. Me la froto mientras la sigo, más despacio, para ver los resultados."

# game/script/hwb_s25a.rpy:460
translate spanish hwb_s25a_8217a97a:

    # "As she cranes around the easel to look, I watch her expression go from excited to overjoyed. Her smile widens into a grin as she grasps the drawing in her hands."
    "Mientras ella se asoma detrás del caballete para mirar, observo cómo su expresión pasa de emocionada a eufórica. Su sonrisa se ensancha hasta convertirse en una mueca mientras agarra el dibujo con las manos."

# game/script/hwb_s25a.rpy:462
translate spanish hwb_s25a_5748e277:

    # Marina "Amber! Look! It’s us!"
    Marina "Эмбер! Смотри! Это мы!"

# game/script/hwb_s25a.rpy:471
translate spanish hwb_s25a_9a49524e:

    # "She flips it around so I can see."
    "Lo voltea para que pueda verlo."

# game/script/hwb_s25a.rpy:475
translate spanish hwb_s25a_b54bf8af:

    # "It’s… Us."
    "Es... Nosotras."

# game/script/hwb_s25a.rpy:477
translate spanish hwb_s25a_fe7afcc9:

    # "The first thing I notice is my boobs. They’re a lot larger than in real life. Same with Marina’s—kinda."
    "Lo primero que noto son mis pechos. Son mucho más grandes que en la vida real. Lo mismo con los de Marina—más o menos."

# game/script/hwb_s25a.rpy:479
translate spanish hwb_s25a_eb581d8c:

    # "Other than that, the drawing is cartoony - we’re recognizable, but our features are exaggerated. Marina’s eyes are almost comically huge."
    "Aparte de eso, el dibujo es caricaturesco—somos reconocibles, pero nuestros rasgos están exagerados. Los ojos de Marina son casi cómicamente enormes."

# game/script/hwb_s25a.rpy:481
translate spanish hwb_s25a_13ba6b87:

    # "In contrast, the buildings behind us in the drawing are sharply defined and realistic."
    "En contraste, los edificios detrás de nosotras en el dibujo están definidos con nitidez y son realistas."

# game/script/hwb_s25a.rpy:487
translate spanish hwb_s25a_934054d1:

    # "Clutching the paper to her chest, Marina sighs a contented smile."
    "Apretando el papel contra su pecho, Marina suspira una sonrisa de satisfacción."

# game/script/hwb_s25a.rpy:489
translate spanish hwb_s25a_83e343b3:

    # Marina "Thank you so much!"
    Marina "Спасибо вам огромное!"

# game/script/hwb_s25a.rpy:491
translate spanish hwb_s25a_d3751d14:

    # "The artist wipes his sweaty palms on his shorts as he stands."
    "El artista se seca las palmas sudorosas en sus pantalones cortos mientras se levanta."

# game/script/hwb_s25a.rpy:493
translate spanish hwb_s25a_0fda5bb8:

    # Artist "My pleasure, my pleasure."
    Artist "Не стоит. Право, не стоит."

# game/script/hwb_s25a.rpy:495
translate spanish hwb_s25a_cac36e99:

    # "And he looks at me expectantly."
    "Y me mira con expectativa."

# game/script/hwb_s25a.rpy:499
translate spanish hwb_s25a_98df6af6:

    # "With a sigh, I pull out my wallet and pass him a pair of wrinkled bills."
    "Con un suspiro, saco mi cartera y le paso un par de billetes arrugados."

# game/script/hwb_s25a.rpy:503
translate spanish hwb_s25a_4835e5df:

    # "I pass it to him with a nod."
    "Se lo paso con un asentimiento."

# game/script/hwb_s25a.rpy:505
translate spanish hwb_s25a_f9930c12:

    # Artist "Y’all have a lovely day now!"
    Artist "Хорошего вам дня!"

# game/script/hwb_s25a.rpy:507
translate spanish hwb_s25a_e03a3423:

    # "With that, he slouches down again and pulls out a cheap-looking paperback novel."
    "Con eso, se encorva de nuevo y saca una novela de bolsillo de aspecto barato."

# game/script/hwb_s25a.rpy:509
translate spanish hwb_s25a_e08904d8:

    # "The drawing is still close to Marina’s chest like a priceless artifact."
    "El dibujo sigue pegado al pecho de Marina como un artefacto invaluable."

# game/script/hwb_s25a.rpy:513
translate spanish hwb_s25a_139757e3:

    # "Every few seconds, she holds it away from her and grins as she looks at it."
    "Cada pocos segundos, lo aleja de ella y sonríe mientras lo mira."

# game/script/hwb_s25a.rpy:515
translate spanish hwb_s25a_4c7bcc31:

    # "That makes it worth the cost."
    "Eso hace que valga la pena el costo."

# game/script/hwb_s25a.rpy:519
translate spanish hwb_s25a_c097b67b:

    # "Finally, Marina rolls up the drawing like a scroll and tucks it under her arm for safekeeping."
    "Finalmente, Marina enrolla el dibujo como un pergamino y lo guarda bajo su brazo para protegerlo."

# game/script/hwb_s25a.rpy:521
translate spanish hwb_s25a_5b515542:

    # "We stand in the shade of the awning while we look up and down the road."
    "Nos paramos a la sombra del toldo mientras miramos a lo largo de la carretera."

# game/script/hwb_s25a.rpy:529
translate spanish hwb_s25a_48017bd8:

    # Marina "We should split up for a little bit."
    Marina "Мы должны ненадолго разделиться."

# game/script/hwb_s25a.rpy:533
translate spanish hwb_s25a_5f1d9671:

    # Amber "What?"
    Amber "Что?"

# game/script/hwb_s25a.rpy:535
translate spanish hwb_s25a_e1285749:

    # "I can’t help but yelp. That was the last thing I was expecting."
    "No puedo evitar dar un grito. Eso era lo último que esperaba."

# game/script/hwb_s25a.rpy:539
translate spanish hwb_s25a_2540e461:

    # Marina "Not for long! There’s just something I wanna do."
    Marina "Ненадолго! Есть кое-что, что я должна сделать."

# game/script/hwb_s25a.rpy:543
translate spanish hwb_s25a_fc8c77c3:

    # Marina "And you can’t be there."
    Marina "И тебе со мной нельзя."

# game/script/hwb_s25a.rpy:545
translate spanish hwb_s25a_2bf8aec0:

    # Amber "Why not?"
    Amber "Почему нет?"

# game/script/hwb_s25a.rpy:549
translate spanish hwb_s25a_7c6a1bf8:

    # "Shuffling in place, Marina looks away."
    "Moviéndose inquieta en su lugar, Marina desvía la mirada."

# game/script/hwb_s25a.rpy:553
translate spanish hwb_s25a_3a5b2e5c:

    # Marina "‘Cause, it’s a surprise."
    Marina "Потому что это сюрприз."

# game/script/hwb_s25a.rpy:557
translate spanish hwb_s25a_e536612d:

    # Amber "Mare, no. This isn’t some small town. This is Las Vegas. What if you get lost, or if some creeper tries to mess with you?"
    Amber "Мари, нет. Это не маленький город. Это Лас-Вегас. Что если ты потеряешься или вляпаешься в какие-нибудь неприятности?"

# game/script/hwb_s25a.rpy:561
translate spanish hwb_s25a_2b91d7ee:

    # Marina "It’ll be fine, Amber. There’s like a million people on this street."
    Marina "Со мной все будет в порядке, Эмбер. Тут миллионы людей на улице."

# game/script/hwb_s25a.rpy:563
translate spanish hwb_s25a_c85f7467:

    # Amber "Yeah, so? That doesn’t mean anything."
    Amber "И что? Это ничего не значит."

# game/script/hwb_s25a.rpy:567
translate spanish hwb_s25a_0cc46d3a:

    # Marina "I mean it, it’ll be fine."
    Marina "Я имею в виду, что все будет хорошо."

# game/script/hwb_s25a.rpy:569
translate spanish hwb_s25a_4fc56b28:

    # "There’s a fire in her voice that takes me by surprise. There’s even a small spark in her eyes - like she’s angry."
    "Hay un fuego en su voz que me toma por sorpresa. Incluso hay una pequeña chispa en sus ojos—como si estuviera enojada."

# game/script/hwb_s25a.rpy:573
translate spanish hwb_s25a_cf8ad07a:

    # "My frown deepens."
    "Mi ceño se frunce más."

# game/script/hwb_s25a.rpy:575
translate spanish hwb_s25a_f17d551b:

    # Amber "But-"
    Amber "Но-"

# game/script/hwb_s25a.rpy:579
translate spanish hwb_s25a_7308ac04:

    # Marina "Seriously. It’s nothing bad, I promise. I just wanna do something, but it’s a surprise for you. So you can’t be there."
    Marina "Серьезно. Ничего плохого не случится, я обещаю. Я просто хочу сделать тебе сюрприз. Поэтому тебе со мной нельзя."

# game/script/hwb_s25a.rpy:583
translate spanish hwb_s25a_5b347eca:

    # "Her face softens."
    "Su rostro se suaviza."

# game/script/hwb_s25a.rpy:585
translate spanish hwb_s25a_a9d5e04d:

    # Marina "Please? It’ll only be a couple hours."
    Marina "Можно? Это займет всего пару часов."

# game/script/hwb_s25a.rpy:589
translate spanish hwb_s25a_eeebc7b1:

    # Amber "Marina, I dunno…"
    Amber "Марина, Я не думаю…"

# game/script/hwb_s25a.rpy:591
translate spanish hwb_s25a_4cf80fd0:

    # "Of all the cities to split up in, this is one of the worst. Not only do we not have a way to contact each other if needed, but the people aren’t the sort you can trust."
    "De todas las ciudades para separarse, esta es una de las peores. No solo no tenemos forma de contactarnos si es necesario, sino que la gente no es de fiar."

# game/script/hwb_s25a.rpy:593
translate spanish hwb_s25a_c9d127de:

    # "If I leave her on her own, there’s a good chance I’d never see her again."
    "Si la dejo sola, hay una gran probabilidad de que nunca la vuelva a ver."

# game/script/hwb_s25a.rpy:595
translate spanish hwb_s25a_3f142734:

    # "But the way she stands there, hands on her hips, looking determined, makes me not wanna argue."
    "Pero la forma en que se para ahí, con las manos en las caderas, con aspecto decidido, hace que no quiera discutir."

# game/script/hwb_s25a.rpy:599
translate spanish hwb_s25a_3f739ce1:

    # "I sigh."
    "Suspiro."

# game/script/hwb_s25a.rpy:603
translate spanish hwb_s25a_f2ffc6cc:

    # Amber "Are you sure?"
    Amber "Ты уверена?"

# game/script/hwb_s25a.rpy:607
translate spanish hwb_s25a_9c817271:

    # Marina "Yeah! I mean it, just give me like… three hours."
    Marina "Да! Я серьезно, просто дай мне примерно… три часа."

# game/script/hwb_s25a.rpy:611
translate spanish hwb_s25a_b8a131ce:

    # Amber "That’s a long time."
    Amber "Это слишком долго."

# game/script/hwb_s25a.rpy:615
translate spanish hwb_s25a_3ffef82d:

    # Marina "You think? I tried to keep it short."
    Marina "Думаешь? Я постаралась наоборот сократить."

# game/script/hwb_s25a.rpy:617
translate spanish hwb_s25a_1b3379d6:

    # "In three hours, she could be snatched into someone’s car and well into Arizona. Or California. Or halfway to Reno."
    "En tres horas, podrían meterla en el auto de alguien y estar bien adentro de Arizona. O California. O a medio camino de Reno."

# game/script/hwb_s25a.rpy:619
translate spanish hwb_s25a_48481dec:

    # "It’s irresponsible of me to let her go."
    "Es irresponsable de mi parte dejarla ir."

# game/script/hwb_s25a.rpy:621
translate spanish hwb_s25a_eeb47f2a:

    # "But I can tell by looking at her that I don’t have a choice."
    "Pero puedo darme cuenta con solo mirarla que no tengo otra opción."

# game/script/hwb_s25a.rpy:625
translate spanish hwb_s25a_fd3492de:

    # Amber "Okay, fine. But can you at least stay on this street?"
    Amber "Ладно, хорошо. Но ты можешь хотя бы остаться на этой улице?"

# game/script/hwb_s25a.rpy:629
translate spanish hwb_s25a_c4078942:

    # Amber "It’s a straight shot back to the Rio where we’re parked. And so it’d be harder to get lost."
    Amber "Эта дорога ведет прямо к Рио, где мы припарковались, так что тут меньше шансов потеряться."

# game/script/hwb_s25a.rpy:633
translate spanish hwb_s25a_308e5d2b:

    # "Marina nods fast."
    "Marina asiente rápido."

# game/script/hwb_s25a.rpy:635
translate spanish hwb_s25a_60e21e61:

    # Marina "That’s fine! I already saw where I need to go. But you’re not allowed to watch, okay?"
    Marina "По рукам! Я как раз видела то, что мне нужно. Но тебе нельзя следить за мной, поняла?"

# game/script/hwb_s25a.rpy:639
translate spanish hwb_s25a_767f2488:

    # Amber "Yeah, yeah. I’ll probably just go back to the car anyway."
    Amber "Да, да. В любом случае я просто вернусь на парковку."

# game/script/hwb_s25a.rpy:643
translate spanish hwb_s25a_7963b82e:

    # "Now she frowns."
    "Ahora frunce el ceño."

# game/script/hwb_s25a.rpy:645
translate spanish hwb_s25a_78dee4b4:

    # Marina "Isn’t there anything you wanna see?"
    Marina "Разве тут нет ничего, на что бы ты хотела посмотреть?"

# game/script/hwb_s25a.rpy:649
translate spanish hwb_s25a_9b32bea4:

    # Amber "Not without you."
    Amber "Без тебя – нет."

# game/script/hwb_s25a.rpy:653
translate spanish hwb_s25a_91358f48:

    # Marina "Aww, Amber."
    Marina "Оуу, Эмбер."

# game/script/hwb_s25a.rpy:655
translate spanish hwb_s25a_3c94511a:

    # "She kicks at the ground."
    "Patea el suelo."

# game/script/hwb_s25a.rpy:659
translate spanish hwb_s25a_4d4bff94:

    # Marina "I guess we don’t have-"
    Marina "Я думаю, мы не должны-"

# game/script/hwb_s25a.rpy:663
translate spanish hwb_s25a_6e8f8596:

    # Amber "No, go on."
    Amber "Нет, все в порядке, иди."

# game/script/hwb_s25a.rpy:667
translate spanish hwb_s25a_e0508e49:

    # Marina "What?"
    Marina "Что?"

# game/script/hwb_s25a.rpy:671
translate spanish hwb_s25a_b120f752:

    # Amber "Just be safe, okay? Don’t do anything silly."
    Amber "Просто будь осторожна, хорошо? И не делай глупостей."

# game/script/hwb_s25a.rpy:673
translate spanish hwb_s25a_430bfe3f:

    # Amber "I guess it’ll be fine for a couple hours."
    Amber "Думаю, за пару часов ничего не случится."

# game/script/hwb_s25a.rpy:677
translate spanish hwb_s25a_f48edd6c:

    # "She takes the drawing in one hand and then hugs me tight. Then, Marina leans up and kisses me on the lips."
    "Toma el dibujo con una mano y luego me abraza fuerte. Entonces, Marina se inclina y me besa en los labios."

# game/script/hwb_s25a.rpy:679
translate spanish hwb_s25a_e3e74cf7:

    # "She pulls away before I can get into it."
    "Se aparta antes de que pueda reaccionar."

# game/script/hwb_s25a.rpy:681
translate spanish hwb_s25a_8cd8505b:

    # Marina "Okay. I’ll see you in a while then."
    Marina "Ладно. Тогда, скоро увидимся."

# game/script/hwb_s25a.rpy:685
translate spanish hwb_s25a_f11d52dc:

    # Amber "Right."
    Amber "Хорошо."

# game/script/hwb_s25a.rpy:687
translate spanish hwb_s25a_95c9d43d:

    # "We stand there, neither of us moving."
    "Nos quedamos ahí, ninguna de las dos se mueve."

# game/script/hwb_s25a.rpy:694
translate spanish hwb_s25a_bb6f8522:

    # "I sigh again, and then trudge back down the road."
    "Suspiro de nuevo, y luego camino de vuelta por el camino arrastrando los pies."

# game/script/hwb_s25a.rpy:696
translate spanish hwb_s25a_76ee2ea5:

    # "I glance back every few steps, but she doesn’t move. Instead, she watches me and waves."
    "Miro hacia atrás cada pocos pasos, pero ella no se mueve. En cambio, me observa y saluda."

# game/script/hwb_s25a.rpy:698
translate spanish hwb_s25a_ff3e8931:

    # "Probably making sure that I keep good on my promise not to follow her."
    "Probablemente asegurándose de que cumplo mi promesa de no seguirla."

# game/script/hwb_s25a.rpy:709
translate spanish hwb_s25a_141d0f51:

    # "As tempting as it is, I’ll let her go for now."
    "Por más tentador que sea, la dejaré ir por ahora."

# game/script/hwb_s25a.rpy:711
translate spanish hwb_s25a_f063e168:

    # "Three hours can’t be that hard."
    "Tres horas no pueden ser tan difíciles."

# game/script/hwb_s25a.rpy:713
translate spanish hwb_s25a_9979a58c:

    # "Right?"
    "¿Verdad?"

